   Bridge:
.              F#                 H
   For all who wait for all who hunger
.                D#m                 C#
   For all whove pained for all who wonder
.               F#               H
   Behold your King behold Messiah
.       D#m        H
   Emmanuel, Emmanuel

[C4]
   Chorus:
.  D#m   H     F#                   C#
   Glory       to the light of the world
.  D#m   H     F#                   C#
   Glory       to the light of the world
.  D#m   H     F#                   C#
   Glory       to the light of the world

