   Bridge:
.               F#              H
   Behold your King behold Messiah
.       D#m        C#
   Emmanuel, Emmanuel

[V3]
 End:
.F#                            H
 The world waits for a miracle the heart longs for a little bit of hope
.  D#m     C#        F#
